<table width="600">
	<tr>
		<td>
			<h1 align="center">DrawSearch</h1>
			<hr>			
		
			<p><b>Developed by:</b><br> Technical University of Bari, Italy </p>
			
			<p>
			<b>Features:</b><br> 
			- <u>Color</u>: Divide into 4x4 grid to form 48-length color vector<br>
			- <u>Shape</u>: Represented by Fourier descriptors.
			</p>
			
			<p>
			<b>Matching:</b><br>
			- Use cosine metric on feature vector (color, shape) between query image and database image<br>
			- Distance calculated based on weighted sum between color vectors and shape descriptors.
			</p>
			
			<p>
			<b>Querying:</b><br>
			- User draws sketch on a canvas and choose color.
			</p>
			
			<p align="center">
			<i>Fig 1. Query window of DrawSearch.</i><br>
			<img border="0" src="images/drawsearch/drawsearch.jpg" width="713" height="416"><i><br>
			&nbsp;</i></p>
			
		</td>
	</tr>
